{"title":"CSS基础","date":"2018-07-28T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 28, 2018","L":"07/28/2018","MM-DD":"07-28"},"thumbnail":"https://blog-1251959181.cos.accelerate.myqcloud.com/taxi_girl.jpg","link":"2018/07/27/imooc_164_2","comments":true,"tags":["CSS","Front-end","Note"],"categories":["Coding","imooc"],"updated":"2024-07-01T17:57:02.534Z","content":"<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.imooc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">慕课网</a>实战课程笔记 —— <a href=\"https://Coding.imooc.com/class/164.html\" target=\"_blank\">全面系统讲解CSS</a></strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"第二章-css基础\">第二章 CSS基础<a title=\"#第二章-css基础\" href=\"#第二章-css基础\"></a></h2>\n<p>Cascading Style Sheet：层叠样式表</p>\n<p>基本规则：<br>\n选择器{<br>\n属性：值；<br>\n属性：值；<br>\n}</p>\n<h3 id=\"选择器\">选择器<a title=\"#选择器\" href=\"#选择器\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>用于匹配HTML元素</li>\n<li>有不同的匹配规则</li>\n<li>多个选择器可以叠加</li>\n<li>分类和权重</li>\n<li>解析方式（从又向左解析）和性能</li>\n<li>值得关注的选择器</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"选择器分类\">选择器分类<a title=\"#选择器分类\" href=\"#选择器分类\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>元素选择器<code>a&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>伪元素选择器<code>::before&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>类选择器<code>.link&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>属性选择器<code>[type=radio]&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>伪类选择器<code>:hover&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>ID选择器<code>#id&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>组合选择器<code>[type=cheakbox]+label&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>否定选择器<code>:not(.link)&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n<li>通用选择器<code>*&#123;&#125;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"选择器权重\">选择器权重<a title=\"#选择器权重\" href=\"#选择器权重\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>ID选择器 +100</li>\n<li>类 属性 伪类 +10</li>\n<li>元素 伪元素 +1</li>\n<li>其他选择器 +0</li>\n<li>权重的计算不进位</li>\n<li>!important优先级最高</li>\n<li>元素属性 优先级高（内联样式）</li>\n<li>相同权重 后写的生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-字体\">非布局样式-字体<a title=\"#非布局样式-字体\" href=\"#非布局样式-字体\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>非布局样式</strong><br>\n字体、字重、颜色、大小、行高<br>\n背景、边框<br>\n滚动、换行<br>\n粗体、斜体、下划线<br>\n其他</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"字体族\">字体族<a title=\"#字体族\" href=\"#字体族\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>serif：衬线字体</li>\n<li>sans-serif：非衬线字体</li>\n<li>monospace：等宽字体</li>\n<li>cursive：手写体</li>\n<li>fantasy：花体</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"多字体：fallback\">多字体：fallback<a title=\"#多字体：fallback\" href=\"#多字体：fallback\"></a></h4>\n<p>首先适配只有一种设备有的字体</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.font-family</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;PingFang SC&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;</span>, serif;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注意：字体用双引号括起来，字体族不用</p>\n<h4 id=\"网络字体、自定义字体\">网络字体、自定义字体<a title=\"#网络字体、自定义字体\" href=\"#网络字体、自定义字体\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">@font-face</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;IF&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">src</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;./IndieFlower.ttf&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.custom-font</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>: IF;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;custom-font&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Hello World<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>远程字体可能会涉及跨域问题</p>\n<h4 id=\"iconfont\">iconfont<a title=\"#iconfont\" href=\"#iconfont\"></a></h4>\n<p>阿里巴巴矢量图标库可生成字体：<a href=\"http://iconfont.cn\">iconfont.cn</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-行高\">非布局样式-行高<a title=\"#非布局样式-行高\" href=\"#非布局样式-行高\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"行高的组成\">行高的组成<a title=\"#行高的组成\" href=\"#行高的组成\"></a></h4>\n<p>行高由line-box组成，line-box的高度由inline-box的高度决定<br>\n背景颜色的高度根据文字大小渲染，由底线和顶线两条线规定<br>\nbase-line：基线（四线格的第三条线对应位置，中文一般为文字底部），默认按基线对齐</p>\n<h4 id=\"行高相关的现象和方案\">行高相关的现象和方案<a title=\"#行高相关的现象和方案\" href=\"#行高相关的现象和方案\"></a></h4>\n<p>垂直对齐方式：vertical-align：top/center/bottom；是按照文字的顶线/底线对齐，而不是顶部/底部<br>\n图片默认按base-line对齐，所以底部会有空白。可通过<code>&lt;vertical-align：top/center/bottom&gt;</code>或<code>&lt;display: block&gt;</code>消除空隙</p>\n<h4 id=\"行高的调整\">行高的调整<a title=\"#行高的调整\" href=\"#行高的调整\"></a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-背景\">非布局样式-背景<a title=\"#非布局样式-背景\" href=\"#非布局样式-背景\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"背景颜色\">背景颜色<a title=\"#背景颜色\" href=\"#背景颜色\"></a></h4>\n<p>background: hsla(0, 100%, 50%, .3);<br>\n色相（0~360）、饱和度、亮度（100%为白色，一般纯色为50%）</p>\n<h4 id=\"渐变色背景\">渐变色背景<a title=\"#渐变色背景\" href=\"#渐变色背景\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">liner-gradient</span>(to right, red, green);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">liner-gradient</span>(<span class=\"number\">45deg</span>, red, blue10%, green50%, yellow);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>线性渐变：角度、起始颜色、相应长度变为相应颜色、最终颜色</p>\n<h4 id=\"多背景叠加\">多背景叠加<a title=\"#多背景叠加\" href=\"#多背景叠加\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">liner-gradient</span>(<span class=\"number\">135deg</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">0</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">49.5%</span>, green <span class=\"number\">49.5%</span>, green <span class=\"number\">50.5%</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">100%</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">liner-gradient</span>(<span class=\"number\">45deg</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">0</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">49.5%</span>, red <span class=\"number\">49.5%</span>, red <span class=\"number\">50.5%</span>, transparent <span class=\"number\">100%</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-size</span>: <span class=\"number\">30px</span> <span class=\"number\">30px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"背景图片和属性（雪碧图）\">背景图片和属性（雪碧图）<a title=\"#背景图片和属性（雪碧图）\" href=\"#背景图片和属性（雪碧图）\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>:red <span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(<span class=\"string\">./test.png</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-repeat</span>: no-repeat/repeat-x/repeat-y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-position</span>: center/<span class=\"number\">20px</span> center/<span class=\"number\">30px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-size</span>: <span class=\"number\">100px</span> <span class=\"number\">50px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>设置背景图片、是否重复、显示位置，可以应用到雪碧图的场景（把所有图标合并减少请求以提高性能）</p>\n<h4 id=\"base64和性能优化\">base64和性能优化<a title=\"#base64和性能优化\" href=\"#base64和性能优化\"></a></h4>\n<p>一段用于显示图片的文本，转换后尺寸会变为原来的4/3<br>\n一般用于小图标</p>\n<h4 id=\"多分辨率适配\">多分辨率适配<a title=\"#多分辨率适配\" href=\"#多分辨率适配\"></a></h4>\n<p>移动端可以通过设置<code>&lt;background-size&gt;</code>把大图片缩小的形式使展示更清晰</p>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-边框\">非布局样式-边框<a title=\"#非布局样式-边框\" href=\"#非布局样式-边框\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"边框的属性：线型-大小-颜色\">边框的属性：线型 大小 颜色<a title=\"#边框的属性：线型-大小-颜色\" href=\"#边框的属性：线型-大小-颜色\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid/dotted/dashed red;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-top-color</span>: red;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-top-style</span>: solid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-top-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-right-color</span>: red;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-right-style</span>: solid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-right-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-bottom-color</span>: red;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-bottom-style</span>: solid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-bottom-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-left-color</span>: red;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-left-style</span>: solid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-left-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-image-source</span>: initial;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-image-slice</span>: initial;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-image-width</span>: initial;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-image-outset</span>: initial;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attribute\">border-image-repeat</span>: initial;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"边框背景图\">边框背景图<a title=\"#边框背景图\" href=\"#边框背景图\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">30px</span> solid transparent;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-image</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(<span class=\"string\">./border.png</span>) <span class=\"number\">30</span> repeat/round;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>round</code>：自动把边框中间部分凑成整数个</p>\n<h4 id=\"边框衔接（三角形）\">边框衔接（三角形）<a title=\"#边框衔接（三角形）\" href=\"#边框衔接（三角形）\"></a></h4>\n<p>边框衔接处为斜切，可以借此实现三角形</p>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-滚动\">非布局样式-滚动<a title=\"#非布局样式-滚动\" href=\"#非布局样式-滚动\"></a></h3>\n<p>滚动行为和滚动条</p>\n<ul>\n<li>visible：滚动条隐藏，超出部分在下面显示</li>\n<li>hidden：滚动条隐藏，超出部分不显示</li>\n<li>scroll：滚动条显示（Windows下滚动条始终显示，mac自动）</li>\n<li>auto：滚动条自动显示</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">overflow</span>: auto;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-文本折行\">非布局样式-文本折行<a title=\"#非布局样式-文本折行\" href=\"#非布局样式-文本折行\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">overflow-wrap</span>: normal/break-word/inherit/initial/unset;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">word-break</span>: normal;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">white-space</span>: normal;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>overflow-wrap(word-wrap)：通用换行控制，是否保留单词</p>\n<ul>\n<li>normal：单词内不换行</li>\n<li>break-word：当单词长度超过容器长度时，可以在单词内换行</li>\n</ul>\n<p>word-break：针对多字节文字，中文句子也是单词</p>\n<ul>\n<li>break-all：单词内换行</li>\n<li>keep-all：单词内不换行，中文遇标点符号允许换行</li>\n</ul>\n<p>white-space：空白处是否换行</p>\n<ul>\n<li>nowrap：不换行</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"非布局样式-装饰性属性\">非布局样式-装饰性属性<a title=\"#非布局样式-装饰性属性\" href=\"#非布局样式-装饰性属性\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"字重（粗体）\">字重（粗体）<a title=\"#字重（粗体）\" href=\"#字重（粗体）\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.class</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-weight</span>: normal;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 默认，对应400 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-weight</span>: bold;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 粗体，对应700 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-weight</span>: bolder;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 更粗，具体值不确定 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-weight</span>: lighter;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 更细，具体值不确定 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">font-weight</span>: <span class=\"number\">100</span>;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 100到900依次增加100，具体表现与浏览器有关 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"斜体\">斜体<a title=\"#斜体\" href=\"#斜体\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>font-style: itatic</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"下划线\">下划线<a title=\"#下划线\" href=\"#下划线\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>text-decoration</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"指针\">指针<a title=\"#指针\" href=\"#指针\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>cursor</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"hack和案例\">hack和案例<a title=\"#hack和案例\" href=\"#hack和案例\"></a></h3>\n<p>兼容低版本IE浏览器，最近用的比较少</p>\n<h3 id=\"面试题\">面试题<a title=\"#面试题\" href=\"#面试题\"></a></h3>\n","prev":{"title":"HTML基础","link":"2018/07/27/imooc_164_1"},"plink":"https://vincenteliang.com/2018/07/27/imooc_164_2/","toc":[{"id":"第二章-css基础","title":"第二章 CSS基础","index":"1","children":[{"id":"选择器","title":"选择器","index":"1.1"},{"id":"非布局样式-字体","title":"非布局样式-字体","index":"1.2"},{"id":"非布局样式-行高","title":"非布局样式-行高","index":"1.3"},{"id":"非布局样式-背景","title":"非布局样式-背景","index":"1.4"},{"id":"非布局样式-边框","title":"非布局样式-边框","index":"1.5"},{"id":"非布局样式-滚动","title":"非布局样式-滚动","index":"1.6"},{"id":"非布局样式-文本折行","title":"非布局样式-文本折行","index":"1.7"},{"id":"非布局样式-装饰性属性","title":"非布局样式-装饰性属性","index":"1.8"},{"id":"hack和案例","title":"hack和案例","index":"1.9"},{"id":"面试题","title":"面试题","index":"1.10"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://vincenteliang.com/2018/07/27/imooc_164_2/\" title=\"CSS基础\">https://vincenteliang.com/2018/07/27/imooc_164_2/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"July 28, 2018","upd